item.title: CVE-2019-3709|2024-09-16T20:21:39.930Z -- dell%20emc -- dell%20emc%20isilonsd%20management%20server
item.description: IsilonSD Management Server 1.1.0 contains a cross-site scripting vulnerability while registering vCenter servers. A remote attacker can trick an admin user to potentially exploit this vulnerability to execute malicious HTML or JavaScript code in the context of the admin user.
